dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field. 2. Fixed capitalization errors in Admin1-3 names. 3. Spanish Admin0 name field now uses UN Short Name "Perú (el)". 4. Holes that are fully contained within Admin boundaries have been filled in. Those bordering admin units that determine borders have been left as-is. 5. Fixed 1 multipart sliver.
